-1693657462.text: "Interestingly, the embryonic lethality of mdm2 and mdmx knockout mice can be rescued by mutant p53 with reduced functions and by genetically modified p53 with restricted p53 expression, allowing studies of Mdm2 and Mdmx dependent temporal and tissue specific phenotypes in those mice [XREF_BIBR - XREF_BIBR]."
